Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.04,0:06:05.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我记得他已经退居二线了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.17,0:06:07.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他会来的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.36,0:06:10.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要得知宝贝女儿被卷了进去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.21,0:06:12.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.81,0:06:14.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你也认识那个日本记者
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.46,0:06:24.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,会场内部状况依然不明
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.26,0:06:28.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大泽
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.62,0:06:31.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大泽！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.61,0:06:33.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}大泽！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.43,0:06:35.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.53,0:06:39.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,难道是跟着他的那个小丫头？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.36,0:06:45.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且她还是铁之斗争代理人的重要朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.67,0:07:04.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他就是大泽贤治吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.23,0:07:07.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们是什么人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.63,0:07:09.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我怎么不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.12,0:07:22.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.78,0:07:23.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.31,0:07:31.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是「{\1c&H0000FF&}蛇{\r}」　大泽贤治的车被炸掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.47,0:07:35.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,副总统阁下
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.51,0:07:38.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我提议将戒备级别提高到3
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.17,0:07:42.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,将军
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.74,0:07:46.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,若没有抗病毒剂 就无法进行救援
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.16,0:07:49.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我申请执行第二套方案
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.84,0:07:51.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,已经别无他法了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.24,0:08:00.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在掌握人民解放军的是方先生吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.89,0:08:01.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.73,0:08:04.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,给我接中国大使
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.01,0:08:10.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再磨蹭下去 我军第七舰队会填满台湾海峡的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.20,0:08:16.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,听到了吗 卑鄙的恐怖分子们
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.19,0:08:18.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们有什么要求
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.89,0:08:20.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,若不互相了解
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.39,0:08:21.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就解决不了任何问题
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.37,0:08:28.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,告诉我 你们为什么要用UA病毒
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.66,0:08:32.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你真忘了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.16,0:08:42.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你这种活在谎言里的女人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.16,0:08:45.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(722,670)\fs35}希望之地
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.16,0:08:45.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,会是那家伙的Canaan吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.64,0:08:48.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,迦南？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.95,0:08:57.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大总统 您不冷吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.28,0:09:03.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那位次官差不多该发臭了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.32,0:09:06.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我就给您开足了冷气
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.27,0:09:09.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,终于开口了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.69,0:09:11.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们是什么人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.14,0:09:13.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,卑贱的恐怖分子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.80,0:09:18.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很遗憾 我们没时间增进感情了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.12,0:09:18.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.55,0:09:21.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再过几个小时
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.44,0:09:23.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们身上的UA病毒就会发作
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.14,0:09:25.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,让你们送命
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.24,0:09:30.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但你优秀的部下们好像不喜欢这样
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.80,0:09:36.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们为尊贵的大总统准备了特别的死法
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.87,0:09:39.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,该不会是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.20,0:09:43.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没错 您引以为豪的隐形轰炸机
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.64,0:09:45.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,两小时前已从关岛起飞了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.36,0:09:51.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,携带着两千磅制导炸弹
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.81,0:09:55.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会这样
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.69,0:09:59.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,完了 一切都完了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.18,0:10:01.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,祝各位一路顺风
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.22,0:10:04.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没关系 那点微不足道的人生
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.47,0:10:07.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有足够时间供你们回味
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.19,0:10:09.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等等！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.03,0:10:15.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,从前有个倒霉的佣兵
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.50,0:10:20.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他接了两次同样的任务
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.25,0:10:25.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把拿不稳枪的小姑娘调教成一方高手
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.83,0:10:27.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,多么无聊的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.37,0:10:30.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,更倒霉的还在后头
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.72,0:10:34.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他的学生被冠以同一个名字
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.11,0:10:39.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是迦南的什么人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.24,0:10:41.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好奇怪的问题
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.43,0:10:46.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也叫迦南
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.92,0:10:48.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,虽然已经舍弃了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.80,0:10:55.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们无论在任何情况下
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.10,0:10:58.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都不能向恐怖分子屈服
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.15,0:11:03.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这才是美国总统高洁的意志
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.14,0:11:07.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,既然如此 我们的道路已经注定
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.83,0:11:14.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们的名字将被永远镌刻在反恐丰碑上
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.09,0:11:21.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,准许轰炸
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.27,0:11:26.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Spirit02 this is AWACS thousand-eye.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.38,0:11:29.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are cleared to commit bombing 310.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.90,0:11:32.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Engage in 230. Visual is clear.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.63,0:11:33.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your weapon is free.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.22,0:11:35.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,May god be with you, guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.78,0:11:42.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Spirit02 will go. Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.04,0:11:51.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,会怎么样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.14,0:11:57.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她会无法救你 无法阻止轰炸
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.48,0:11:59.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,坠入无底深渊呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.97,0:12:05.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还是克服一切 再次挡在我的面前呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.18,0:12:08.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在看来 似乎是后者
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.50,0:12:11.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿尔法鲁多大人 到时间了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.28,0:12:12.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.17,0:12:18.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.22,0:12:23.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,挣扎到最后吧 两位
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.17,0:12:28.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,两位？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.73,0:12:49.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大泽贤治被杀了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.63,0:12:53.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,束手无策的白宫打算使用禁招
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.32,0:12:55.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,胡说 这不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.99,0:12:56.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,会引发战争的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.10,0:13:00.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,中国政府也不是团结一致的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.90,0:13:03.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对上海派来说 这是个好机会
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.27,0:13:06.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可恶 一个个都疯了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.08,0:13:08.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.75,0:13:12.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个房间还能用吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.36,0:13:16.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thousand-eye, Spirit02.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.44,0:13:19.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ETA target 20 minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.29,0:13:37.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是很久没用了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.05,0:13:42.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,与NSA协同作战时 对方擅自设置的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.01,0:13:42.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,之后就没动过
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.55,0:13:44.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,又不能当大件垃圾处理掉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.16,0:13:50.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,虽然老了一代 但应该能行
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.33,0:13:52.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你没事吧 玛丽亚
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.15,0:13:54.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,迦南 听我说
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.23,0:13:54.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嘘
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.27,0:13:58.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这样就能和外界联络了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.46,0:13:59.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.15,0:14:03.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等等 地下还有UA病毒感染者
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.36,0:14:05.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,UA病毒？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.52,0:14:08.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且 轰炸机似乎正飞往这边
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.55,0:14:10.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,虽然我不太明白
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.75,0:14:15.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,总算接通了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.95,0:14:17.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你有什么好办法
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.26,0:14:20.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看来你已经搞清状况了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.50,0:14:22.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那么 告诉我你现在的位置
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.53,0:14:25.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这里有很多显示器
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.00,0:14:29.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,主控制室 正好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.29,0:14:32.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我这就连网过去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.71,0:14:33.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,稍等
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.56,0:14:36.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你要做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.48,0:14:40.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要入侵美军的导航卫星群
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.68,0:14:43.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,放开我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.74,0:14:45.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们很烦耶
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.14,0:15:02.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事 会场里还有人…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.32,0:15:05.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可能被舍弃了 正抽泣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.87,0:15:11.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快点 来个high tension
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.40,0:15:13.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知道
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.89,0:15:16.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,high tension来咯！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.75,0:15:19.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,走
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.07,0:15:24.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿尔法鲁多大人 梁琪大人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.75,0:15:25.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没时间了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.42,0:15:27.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要管她了？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.69,0:15:29.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 是舍弃
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.26,0:15:37.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.87,0:15:42.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ETA target 2 minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.01,0:15:56.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我已经连上你那边了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.26,0:15:59.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,传送入侵卫星的资料
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.82,0:16:03.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要我读出什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.01,0:16:07.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,刚才你用手机使用的功能
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.98,0:16:09.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,GPS？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.13,0:16:10.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,聪明
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.79,0:16:13.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我会尽量扫除障碍
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.41,0:16:17.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但还没能最终锁定范围
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.65,0:16:20.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,从刚才起 我就完全听不懂你的话
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.04,0:16:23.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就算用电波干扰麻痹GPS
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.22,0:16:27.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还有惯性制导 误差在30米以内
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.86,0:16:30.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,需要彻底变更目标
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.92,0:16:31.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以说 你想…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.64,0:16:59.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,副总统阁下 是大泽贤治
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.64,0:17:01.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不可能 他不是死了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.74,0:17:18.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Holly shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.87,0:17:21.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,迦南？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.21,0:17:22.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,来了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.48,0:17:27.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Locked on target and standing by, 20 miles.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.87,0:17:35.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,上帝啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.12,0:17:38.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,God help us all.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.43,0:17:45.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bomb’s away. At 35 secends.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.55,0:17:47.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,轰炸中止！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.05,0:17:51.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会这样…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.14,0:17:55.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,投了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.55,0:17:57.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们投弹了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.14,0:18:00.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,距离命中还有近40秒时间
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.05,0:18:01.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,集中精神
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.58,0:18:16.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,迦南
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.32,0:18:42.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,给我赶上！
