Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.03,0:18:49.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\fs70\t(0,200,1,\fs45)\t(710,910,1,\fs1)}4
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.39,0:18:51.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\fs70\t(0,200,1,\fs45)\t(700,900,1,\fs1)}3
