Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.74,0:18:53.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\fs70\t(0,200,1,\fs45)\t(580,780,1,\fs1)}1
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.84,0:18:54.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\fs70\t(0,200,1,\fs40)\t(840,1040,1,\fs1)}Impact!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.61,0:19:06.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大泽…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.62,0:19:16.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大泽！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.49,0:19:30.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,迦南？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.71,0:19:31.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,迦南！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.89,0:19:37.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你没事吧 振作点！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.62,0:19:39.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,玛丽亚…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.72,0:19:41.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,炸弹呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.91,0:19:47.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个… 既然我们还活着…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.96,0:19:53.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,迦南！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.46,0:19:56.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,迦南迦南迦南！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.10,0:19:57.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害 太厉害了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.39,0:19:59.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你做了什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.24,0:20:03.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 我只是创造了契机
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.87,0:20:05.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,虽然够乱来的…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.55,0:20:10.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个… 我听不太懂
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.76,0:20:12.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不管怎么说 迦南你太伟大了！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.90,0:20:15.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}打偏了？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.22,0:20:20.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,临近命中时 GPS制导装置受到不明干扰
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.81,0:20:22.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,未能直接命中
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.01,0:20:25.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,落在了距目标五十米处
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.26,0:20:28.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不知该不该庆幸打偏一事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.49,0:20:32.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没错 不允许失败
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.43,0:20:37.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,正因如此 才要一击必杀
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.98,0:20:40.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,让轰炸机撤退
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.25,0:20:46.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Spirit02 abort mission
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.51,0:20:48.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,RTB immediately. I repeat
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.85,0:20:51.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.76,0:20:54.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你这可怕的女人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.90,0:21:00.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但做这种义工 对你有什么好处？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.12,0:21:02.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为了直面过去
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.80,0:21:06.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,容我反问一句
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.70,0:21:13.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,逃避过去 一直逃避下去 就能得到真正的救赎吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.82,0:21:24.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,随你喜欢？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.04,0:21:27.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那不可能 姐姐大人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.37,0:21:30.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这已经不是喜欢的问题了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.07,0:21:33.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爱是… 爱是…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.10,0:21:35.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,无法抑制的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.42,0:21:41.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太阳公公 风儿 氧气
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.71,0:21:42.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我还活着！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.98,0:21:53.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,迦南？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.36,0:21:58.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,颜色… 看不到颜色了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.21,0:21:59.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.74,0:22:04.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不… 这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.94,0:22:08.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真正的颜色
